cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM 

The paper deals with object detection using deep learning techniques, specifically for autonomous vehicles. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) domains. The use of Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) for image-to-image translation is a popular technique in the field of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves the creation of an artificial dataset, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM) research.
